Text:
Sorry about the speed. It is the best I can do. Cap your upload speed if you prefer.

When people don't seed, then I have to seed old torrents too, and that cuts my ability and speed to seed new stuff. So, your seeding helps my speed! Thanks for helping out.

Thanks Frankie, your generosity has led me to enjoy new films in a genre I love.
 I will do my best to provide as much seeding as I can with my modest means.
Reseed by uploader completed December 2011. Please seed.
